		<title>Landmark Mayo Clinic study finds stenting reduces stroke risk in people with carotid artery narrowing</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/landmark-mayo-clinic-study-finds-stenting-reduces-stroke-risk-in-people-with-carotid-artery-narrowing/
		
